#about.about-selerity
  header.container-fluid
    .row.header-background-image
      .header-background-color
      .header-content
        .left-corner
        p.text-center Selerity is fundamentally changing the way people discover
          | relevant information by bringing the age of context to the business
          | professional. Our mission is to empower professionals with relevant
          | content based on their individual workflow and what's happening in
          | the world in real-time.
        .right-corner
  #about-nav.about-nav
    nav.container
      .row
        ul(role='navigation')#about-nav.row.navigation.list-inline.list-unstyled
          li(data-section='1')
