              | Contact Us
  section.intro.about-section
    .container
      .row
        .part-intro
          h3.text-uppercase.section-title about
          p Selerity is the first contextual content recommendation 
            | company for enterprise applications. We deliver high-quality, 
            | personalized content that is engaging and actionable optimized 
            | business professionals in specific verticals such as finance. 
            | Using Selerity, enterprise messaging platforms, publishers, 
            | research & banking portals, and e-brokers can rapidly incorporate 
            | high-quality 3rd party and proprietary content personalized 
            | to their users’ workflow and interests. The result is higher 
            | engagement, traffic, and customer satisfaction.
        .part-intro
          h3.text-uppercase.section-title history
          p Selerity began as a real-time search and breaking news platform 
            | for institutional and retail investors. Our customers include 
            | some of the most sophisticated electronic trading firms, asset 
            | managers, and retail investors operating in the market today. 
            | In only a few years, Selerity established itself as the industry’s 
            | leading real-time event data provider, but we had aspirations of 
            | expanding beyond our core market. Using our deep understanding of 
            | real-time news, unstructured content analytics, and the needs of 
            | information professionals, we began working on the industry's 
            | first contextual content recommendation service. The result, 
            a(href="products.html") Selerity Context
            | , a platform that dynamically recommends relevant content based 
            | on a deep understanding of importance and user intent.

